languages.text: "Не дорос{mf||ла} ты, чтобы мне велеть. Злишься, да? Хорошо. Злость — это сила. Как поднакопишь достаточно, разыщи меня, сразимся как равные, посмотрим кто кого. А пока прощай. Моя охота окончена".

"You've got a long way to go before you can order me around. Are you angry? Good. Anger is power. When you build up enough of it, come and find me, and we shall fight as equals and see who comes out on top. Farewell for now. My hunt is over."

languages.text: «Mucho tiene que mejorar para permitirse darme órdenes a mí. ¿Está {mf|enfadado|enfadada}? Bien. La ira es poder. Cuando tenga el suficiente, venga a buscarme y lucharemos como iguales para decidir quién queda por encima. De momento, esto es un adiós. Mi cacería ha terminado».

languages.text: “打算随我发号施令？你恐怕还有很长的路要走。你生气了？很好，愤怒就是力量。等你积蓄了足够的力量，就来找我吧，咱们一对一决斗，看看谁更厉害。但现在，再见了，我的狩猎已经结束了。”
languages.original_text: "You've got a long way to go before you can order me around. Are you angry? Good. Anger is power. When you build up enough of it, come and find me, and we shall fight as equals and see who comes out on top. Farewell for now. My hunt is over."

traits.locale_text: “在你能对我发号施令前，你还有很长的路要走。你生气了吗？很好，愤怒就是力量。等你积蓄了足够的力量，就来找我吧，咱们一对一决斗，看看谁更厉害。但现在，再见了，我的狩猎已经结束了。”

languages.text: « Vous n'êtes pas près de me donner des ordres, novice. Êtes-vous en colère ? Tant mieux. La colère est source de puissance. Quand vous en aurez accumulé suffisamment, venez me trouver ; nous combattrons d'égal à égal et nous verrons alors qui est le plus fort. Pour l'heure, au revoir. Ma chasse est terminée. »
languages.original_text: "You've got a long way to go before you can order me around. Are you angry? Good. Anger is power. When you build up enough of it, come and find me, and we shall fight as equals and see who comes out on top. Farewell for now. My hunt is over."

traits.locale_text: « Vous n'êtes pas près de me donner des ordres, novice. Quoi, ça vous énerve ? Tant mieux. La colère est source de puissance. Quand vous en aurez accumulé suffisamment, venez me trouver ; nous combattrons d'égal à égal et nous verrons alors qui est le plus fort. Pour l'heure, au revoir. Ma chasse est terminée. »

languages.text: 「俺に命令する前に、お前は長い道のりを歩まなければならない。怒っているのか？いいぜ。怒りは力だ。それが十分に溜まったら、俺を探しに来て、対等に戦って、どちらが上かを確かめようじゃないか。さらばだ。俺の狩りは終わった」
languages.original_text: "You've got a long way to go before you can order me around. Are you angry? Good. Anger is power. When you build up enough of it, come and find me, and we shall fight as equals and see who comes out on top. Farewell for now. My hunt is over."

languages.text: "Ihr habt noch einen weiten Weg vor Euch, ehe Ihr mich herumkommandieren könnt. Seid Ihr zornig? Gut. Zorn ist Macht. Wenn Ihr genug davon aufgebaut habt, kommt zu mir, dann kämpfen wir als Ebenbürtige und sehen, wer die Oberhand behält. Vorerst auf Wiedersehen. Meine Jagd ist vorbei."
languages.original_text: "You've got a long way to go before you can order me around. Are you angry? Good. Anger is power. When you build up enough of it, come and find me, and we shall fight as equals and see who comes out on top. Farewell for now. My hunt is over."

languages.text: "Bana öyle kolay kolay emir veremezsin. Öfkelendin mi? Güzel. Öfke güçtür. Yeterli öfkeyi topladığında gel beni bul. Denk olarak dövüşür ve kimin zaferle ayrılacağını görürüz. Şimdilik elveda. Benim avım sona erdi."
languages.original_text: "You've got a long way to go before you can order me around. Are you angry? Good. Anger is power. When you build up enough of it, come and find me, and we shall fight as equals and see who comes out on top. Farewell for now. My hunt is over."
